[{"id":969939,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<h2>最近邮箱莫名其妙收到某些项目的无脑推广, 这些项目可以说与我毫不相关, 我从来没关注过; 没事就给你发几封垃圾邮件.</h2>\n<h3>其中 <a href=\"https://github.com/cskefu/cskefu\" rel=\"nofollow\">春松客服</a> 反馈之后得到的回复是这样:</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"d8AYmWC\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d8AYmWC.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"g078u6M\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g078u6M.png\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"21HpEUw\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/21HpEUw.png\"/></p>\n<p>原 issue <a href=\"https://github.com/cskefu/cskefu/issues/931\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/cskefu/cskefu/issues/931</a></p>\n<h2>就是说在某些人的逻辑里: 你在 GitHub 公开了邮箱就表示你同意了他们给你邮箱无脑灌任何邮件, 而且你不接受显得你很有问题???</h2>\n<h3>我不知道是我个人问题还是咋回事, 我想问问各位也是这么觉得的么?</h3>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969939","replies":290,"created_ts":1693528221,"created":"08:30:21","title":"各位在 GitHub 公开邮箱就代表你们愿意接受各种无关项目的推广信息么?","author":"mritd","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mritd","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/be45/d0c4/124524_mini.png?m=1665565105"},{"id":969972,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>以前买的这个 iphone ，买完后马上贴了膜，最近膜进水了，我不得已撕掉了，发现屏幕清晰了很多，显示效果也更好了。</p>\n<p>但是不贴膜又担心屏幕会刮花，不可逆。很纠结，想着能多用几年的。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969972","replies":152,"created_ts":1693532758,"created":"09:45:58","title":"大家买完手机后会第一时间贴膜、戴壳子吗","author":"hekouwang123","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hekouwang123","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4bc866d6b02f79a26ad94e602ceb3dc5?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":969938,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119","description":"<p>做了一个阿里云盘的搜索引擎，体验地址<a href=\"https://pan.justin3go.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">pan.justin3go.com</a></p>\n<p>技术细节可以看这两篇文章</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://justin3go.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/2023/08/29%E4%BD%A0%E6%9D%A5%E4%BD%A0%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%98%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">你来你也可以做一个网盘搜索引擎</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://justin3go.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/2023/08/17%E6%B5%85%E8%B0%88%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">浅谈搜索引擎原理</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>简化了很多搜索引擎的复杂策略，但也算是一个微型搜索引擎了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969938","replies":92,"created_ts":1693527941,"created":"08:25:41","title":"做了一个阿里云盘的搜索引擎","author":"Justin3go","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Justin3go","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47aa/34d5/645300_mini.png?m=1692889724"},{"id":970060,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>房贷首套首付降到 20%了，能有什么效果，各位预言家</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970060","replies":88,"created_ts":1693544110,"created":"12:55:10","title":"房贷首套首付降到 20%了","author":"kingpo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kingpo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9d47/5c42/444293_mini.png?m=1683618000"},{"id":969951,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1644885960","description":"<div class=\"embedded_video_wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gQ6zIHHMlSs\" class=\"embedded_video\" allowfullscreen=\"\" type=\"text/html\" id=\"ytplayer\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969951","replies":83,"created_ts":1693530496,"created":"09:08:16","title":"新款 model 3 评测","author":"yazinnnn","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yazinnnn","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a524fa152f42c833f1e93100e07a12af?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970059,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>相册从来不保存任何照片/视频   </p>\n<p>拍的照片不管多少   挑挑拣拣发个朋友圈   全删光    几乎不会保留超过 1 周时间</p>\n<p>手机相册 99%的时间都是空荡荡</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970059","replies":78,"created_ts":1693543856,"created":"12:50:56","title":"你们手机相册会保存大量照片/视频吗?","author":"bootvue","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/bootvue","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/52edce86633f4c335d03998cce737f6e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":969983,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"目前遇到的状况<br /><br />   1- 对于陌生路段不敢走，怕走错逆向车道（之前夜晚开车差点逆向）<br />   2- 看导航走错，比如前方还有几百米右转，错过路口或者提前右转，把握不住这个距离感<br />   3- 陌生隧道容易走错，里面有分叉的时候，有的隧道入口靠左还是靠右行使影响隧道里岔路口变道的难易程度<br />   ...<br />   <br />  <br />虽然目前开车看导航也会提前看，具体到路口虽然导航有详细弹窗显示，但面对复杂路口的时候还是会走错，问一下大家该如何高效的有遇见性的看导航地图来积累不走错路的经验","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969983","replies":76,"created_ts":1693533777,"created":"10:02:57","title":"开车时间不久的司机如何高效的有遇见性的看地图导航","author":"rivercherdeeeeee","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rivercherdeeeeee","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4b10f242f87305c0a9ecc911f40d25a4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970171,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>当然，除去吃喝拉撒睡和打游戏。</p>\n<p>如何坚持的？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970171","replies":69,"created_ts":1693562063,"created":"17:54:23","title":"你有哪些长期（两年以上）坚持做的事情吗？","author":"libasten","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/libasten","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f6d4baad62e4ee124d392af83650f37d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":969955,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1651565926","description":"<p>链接： <a href=\"https://lore.kernel.org/netdev/20230829150539.6f998d1f@kernel.org/T/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://lore.kernel.org/netdev/20230829150539.6f998d1f@kernel.org/T/</a>\ncompany patch 数排名</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/47uvZGx.png\"/></p>\n<p>review 得分排名</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qb91csB.png\"/> </p>\n<p>到国外刷存在感式丢人</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969955","replies":66,"created_ts":1693531194,"created":"09:19:54","title":"看到 6.6 netdev 贡献排名，笑死，国内大厂猛刷 patch 数量， review 都是负分，啥时候能不倦 kpi 了","author":"JohnSmith","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/JohnSmith","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/271a/299f/48772_mini.png?m=1671115432"},{"id":969965,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"麒麟 9000S 几个感觉可以解惑的部分，经过 Dieshot 验证，可以放心食用。<br /><br />Q：是所谓 14+14 ＞ 7nm 吗？<br />A：不是，单 die （芯片），研判非三星工艺，非台积电工艺，整体密度和台积电 N7 类似。<br /><br />Q：光刻机是什么？<br />A：不是 SSA600/SSA800 ，没有看出尼康机台相关特征，有类似 SMASH 系统痕迹。<br /><br />Q：CPU/GPU 是自研的吗？<br />A：没有在过去芯片中看到类似的 CPU 大核中核/GPU 结构。<br /><br />Q：CPU 的 smt （超线程）是真的吗？<br />A：是真的，TSV200 （之前认为 110 迭代是 120 ）疑似命名，和服务器端类似，在移动端使用原因未知。<br /><br />Q：是集成基带吗？<br />A：是。<br /><br />附加：<br /><br />国产 hb pop 技术突破<br /><br />来源： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://weibo.com/6202265538/Nh9JM6mTv#comment\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://weibo.com/6202265538/Nh9JM6mTv#comment</a><br /><br /><br />来自微博评论的总结<br /><br />「我来总结 1.单 die 非堆叠，工艺接近 n7 2.确定 1980di duv 生产 3.泰山架构和笛卡尔架构，泰山基于 arm 指令集自研，笛卡尔新自研 gpu 架构 4.超线程有(但我感觉意义不明，后续应该会取消。) 5.集成基带(而且是新技术) 附加，国产的 Fan-Out Wafer-Level Packaging 晶圆级封装技术突破。」","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969965","replies":65,"created_ts":1693532304,"created":"09:38:24","title":"经过 Dieshot 验证，关于麒麟 9000S 的信息","author":"EmotionV","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/EmotionV","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dd98/ca41/117373_mini.png?m=1693532428"},{"id":970009,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>为什么每次自己放的屁，还有酸脚，都要猛吸几口，意犹未尽。\n但是别人的哪怕是最亲近的人放的屁，会让人犯恶心？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970009","replies":62,"created_ts":1693536834,"created":"10:53:54","title":"为什么自己的屁是香的，别人的屁是臭的？","author":"StephenCurryII","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/StephenCurryII","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6113197e2e1613128c833690cd8f24f0?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970005,"node":"游戏","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/games","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927","description":"<p>B 社背靠微软这座大山，搞出来的东西还是一坨。这是不是说明了在微软工作是真的爽，旗下养得全是闲人。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970005","replies":56,"created_ts":1693535508,"created":"10:31:48","title":"星空终于还是暴死了","author":"Salticey","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Salticey","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c608/4947/389889_mini.png?m=1678550703"},{"id":969994,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<p>很早之前关注过副业这个话题并在本站分享过一篇<a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/848072\" rel=\"nofollow\">程序员开展副业的一些思考、参考</a></p>\n<p>当时引起了不少朋友的思考，甚至我自己也创建了两个微信群，然而随着我经营的一家软件公司倒闭（详情请见 <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/653380203\" rel=\"nofollow\">花 2000 万开一家软件公司并倒闭了，是一种怎样的体验</a>），我自己都默默退出了群聊，但我没想到这是一门已经被玩出花的生意。</p>\n<p>我们先通过一张图片推测一组数据：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"WX20230901-095812@2x.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/817YEL3tPeUpABN.png\"/></p>\n<p>9 块 9 入群，这是 6 群，之前的群是已经加满。</p>\n<p>然后再看另一个做的体量更大的：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"WX20230901-100405@2x.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/kNJYE42WjexP9Lg.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"WX20230901-094924@2x.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/i3mfMasXWxIhJGw.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"WX20230901-100204@2x.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/L8CVYle3PTNFKkt.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"WX20230901-094842@2x.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/Zga6TYOlKPjHEpu.png\"/></p>\n<p>简单直接的宣传口号，实际的项目却是教你怎么用 GPT 类的工具。</p>\n<p>那么，群里是否有什么有价值的项目呢，潜水了今天原本群一直挺安静的，几乎没什么人发消息，昨天夜里突然被刷屏，我以为是有什么好项目爆了，赶紧打开看看，好家伙，直接上图大家自行欣赏：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"WechatIMG36.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/FxRjoDVIZNM7XQW.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"WechatIMG37.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/lP8mZEeokbq3ALO.jpg\"/>\n<img alt=\"WechatIMG35.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s2.loli.net/2023/09/01/WrL3QAPsRMaulwU.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>原来是群友在激烈地互骂。来龙去脉我简单地归纳一下就是这两人私聊交换项目，原本谈好的条件是拿一个搞钱项目免费换对方的，但是其中一人却要收费 2980 ，导致对方破防。</p>\n<p>如果你在知乎小红书抖音等平台搜索这类付费粉丝群，你会发现数量相当庞大。</p>\n<p>ChatGPT/SD 等 AI 工具对程序员来说早就不是新鲜词，而且也不需要自己亲自去教学，搬运一下谁不会呢？</p>\n<p>那么，对于只想搞钱的朋友，是不是可以广撒网试试，搞个付费粉丝群/小程序然后多平台推广呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969994","replies":56,"created_ts":1693534635,"created":"10:17:15","title":"富业观察（1） - 程序员能实操的一个副业，付费加群居然能搞几十万","author":"babyoung","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/babyoung","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4df4/9b56/103835_mini.png?m=1693440490"},{"id":969948,"node":"电动汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1643940920","description":"看价格也出来了，涨价了？不是 20 万？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969948","replies":54,"created_ts":1693529945,"created":"08:59:05","title":"新款 model3 有人冲吗","author":"xh20201111","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xh20201111","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b23762c43af3f62f4dc8a86381d2fe0a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970072,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"1.去年 iPhone14 系列发布的时候，我第一时间抢的是 iPhone14 ，因为我之前用的是 iPhone8plus ，就觉得太大了，手感不好，觉得 14 的大小刚好。但是后面经过了解考虑我取消订单，并且换成了 iPhone14pro Max ，这导致我等了一个月才收到手机（那种迫切希望快点拿到手机的心情谁懂）。用过 iPhone14pro Max 之后，觉得太香了！优点：续航太顶了，正常使用一天电量都用不完（不用老是充电的快乐谁懂），玩游戏看视频体验比较好，很爽（其实不管用手机做什么都会比较爽，这就是大屏的快乐）。缺点：没有（可能有点小贵）。预算没那么高可以买 plus 。<br />2.有些人不选择 iPhone14pro Max 是因为太大太重，手感不好。这个时候手机壳就很重要了，我当时想这么大的手机，肯定要买个手感好一点的手机壳，然后我选择了官方皮革壳，手感无敌！还巨轻！拿着戴着官方皮革的 iPhone14pro Max 一点也不觉得累赘。可能有人会介意皮革会包浆，也觉得贵。我觉得皮革盘过之后有复古味道，别有一番风味。而且你买普通手机壳几十块钱，换多几次也差不多钱了，官方皮革的可以用好久，目前我的已经使用一年。<br />3.抢购的话推荐在 Apple Store ，可以到店取货（最快）或者快递，提前填好地址等个人信息，付款方式，收藏好抢购的型号，具体可以搜搜小红书之类的<br />4.使用一年 iPhone14pro Max 之后，感受就是为什么没有早点买 pro Max 系列，iPhone13pro Max 上市就应该买的！<br />5.有时候我们会一味不愿尝试新事物，觉得自己使用过的拥有的就是最好的，换一个角度，勇敢去尝试，你可能会发现外面的世界更美好。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970072","replies":52,"created_ts":1693546180,"created":"13:29:40","title":"给准备买 iPhone15 系列的 v 友一些建议","author":"mariljacksoa","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mariljacksoa","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0e34b31c32948d8bcd83867f5585e0b9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":969968,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>合作的公司给开发一个程序，今天系统突然报错，找运维检查发现服务器某些文件内容空了</p>\n<p>联系这家公司的程序员查原因，发现 git 上改了这段内容，不太懂这段代码的意义是什么？</p>\n<p>顺便求助一下如何检查项目中有类似的代码</p>\n<img alt=\"Xnip2023-09-01_09-37-18.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s1.locimg.com/2023/09/01/d15482332f078.jpg\" title=\"Xnip2023-09-01_09-37-18.jpg\"/>","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/969968","replies":50,"created_ts":1693532523,"created":"09:42:03","title":"请教一下这种代码的目的是什么，如何检查出来","author":"kemikemian","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kemikemian","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02e0571e9680a9e62904aec8eb9c20d0?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970026,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<p>最近因为手头紧，打算 iPhone 12 换成 iPhone XS 。听到最近华为发布了 mate60 pro 。也是 5g 手机。在前两年的时候，就有运营商对 4g 进行降速。就是 4g 比原来稍微满了一点，但不会影响正常使用。那两年是华为被制裁的时候，运营商为了给华为一些面子，不会把 4g 限速太狠。尤其是现在华为恢复发布 5g 手机了。那些华为用户又可以用 5g 了。请问现在运营商对 4g 的降速会不会越来越狠。使网速变得比 3g 还慢。好像现在广东电信都对 2g 动刀子关闭 2g 了。4g 还会继续继续被狠狠地阉割吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970026","replies":44,"created_ts":1693538232,"created":"11:17:12","title":"mate60 pro 发布后，运营商对 4g 限速会不会更狠？","author":"pengyuedenai1234","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pengyuedenai1234","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4bcb966c4133dd416d891b959ca86035?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970244,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970244","replies":43,"created_ts":1693580143,"created":"22:55:43","title":"牙痛真恶心啊,艹,才 30 出头啊,艹","author":"chenqh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chenqh","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d8be1ee891483e0287a7350aae996608?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970058,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>在用 win10 LTSC 2021 。2021/12/05 日安装。</p>\n<p>最近发现 C 盘快爆了。。。手痒想重装系统。但是感觉太麻烦了，又不是不能用。。。</p>\n<p>现在 win11 也没 LTSC ，所以要上 win11 么？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970058","replies":42,"created_ts":1693543683,"created":"12:48:03","title":"大家多久重装一次系统？","author":"wangweitung","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangweitung","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/59d1/300b/391322_mini.png?m=1642945423"},{"id":970045,"node":"电动汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ev","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/bdb1/06a0/1034_mini.png?m=1643940920","description":"<p>rt\n还能涨，是没想到的！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970045","replies":42,"created_ts":1693540317,"created":"11:51:57","title":"特斯拉 Model3 新款改动很大吗？","author":"xuelulu","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xuelulu","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ae51716289bca304bf3966dadd3ee591?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970155,"node":"游戏","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/games","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927","description":"<p>最好是：1.你们最近或者一直都在玩的。\n2.（如果是手游）竖屏可以解决，单手也行。\n3.（如果是手游）希望可以几分钟一局那种碎片化的 如果非常好玩也可以无视这一点 hhh\n自身情况跟口味:之前在玩的 FARLIGHT 84 （ PC ）突然登不上了..也不想充加速器..金灿灿朋友在玩我也玩了 总感觉坚持不下去（年纪大了 CSGO APEX 反应大不如前）原神突然之间失去兴趣也删除了 但感觉有一天会安装回去的 本来想回坑玩一下 SUPERCELL 的皇室冲突(原来跟国际服断开了 变成企鹅特供版就不爽) 荒野乱斗也觉得新鲜劲过了</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970155","replies":39,"created_ts":1693559802,"created":"17:16:42","title":"大家工作生活挺忙的，有什么好的游戏推荐呢？","author":"Syuusaku","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Syuusaku","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b821/20fb/169235_mini.png?m=1644404645"},{"id":970142,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<p>近期考虑跳槽，基本上中小厂都是有加班这种硬性要求，要不就是外包公司。身边有一两个比较大佬级别的朋友在外企。工作似乎十分自由，没有考勤，只需完成手中任务就好。遂考虑尝试一下发简历给外企。但是英语水平比较垃圾。是属于四级刚过线，之后就再也没用过英语的人了。有各个外企面试经历或者在外企工作的 v 友可以分享下，入职外企所需要的英语能力吗。谢谢！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970142","replies":38,"created_ts":1693556900,"created":"16:28:20","title":"外企英语大概要什么水平才有机会入职","author":"Renco","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Renco","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8530/7718/402540_mini.png?m=1637991602"},{"id":970112,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1692078075","description":"<ol>\n<li>2023 年 9 月，刚好入职一年，想自己做一个思考，从大学一路走来没有方向，学的东西很少，基础差。</li>\n<li>经过工作的一年，逐渐认识到了自己想要什么，想进大厂，进大厂是为了拿高薪，去更大的、更专业的公司看看，为职业道路添砖加瓦，这是在我当前认知下设立的目标。</li>\n<li>在现在的公司，感觉身边的人技术不强，都在公司自研的一些工具和框架下开发，更关注于业务（我对公司的业务不感兴趣），我理解现在开发的状态有点类似于“低代码”，所以可能在工作中很少有偏技术的活，更多是简单和重复的体力活，虽然干着蛮舒服的，不怎么需要动脑，但我知道自己离技术越来越远。</li>\n<li>未来想去大厂，有点不知道如何准备，迷茫。</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>想请教 V 站的前辈们，希望能有幸得到一些指导或分享。有类似经历或刚工作不久的朋友也欢迎留言。谢谢大家的时间！</strong></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970112","replies":31,"created_ts":1693553015,"created":"15:23:35","title":"本科毕业， Java 开发一年，在中小公司，想提升自己，进大厂，拿高薪，求指导和分享","author":"v2Berg","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2Berg","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5955a386a8ca5b426530455d45c767dd?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":970205,"node":"投资","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706","description":"<p>沪深交易所都发布关于量化（程序化交易）的监管方案，本周在这么多政策利好的情况下，市场表现离预期差了很远，市场主要矛头似乎指向了量化。前几天还流传了量化大佬 2.8 亿买豪宅，舆论压力下 2.6 亿紧急卖出的花边。</p>\n<p>量化本来是有利于市场交易活跃度的，但是因为 t+1 的政策和融资融券的存在能变相让量化机构能做到 t+0 ？所以在震荡行情下量化机构反复收割韭菜？（真实性有待验证）。</p>\n<p>可以预见上头是真的希望 A 股涨起来，只能说短期靠政策，长期还是看经济发展。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/970205","replies":25,"created_ts":1693569574,"created":"19:59:34","title":"证监会加强对量化的监管","author":"Skifary","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Skifary","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c2ae/285c/202170_mini.png?m=1692253972"}]